    <section id="id5935714">
      <title>SOUTH AFRICAN SONGS RELATING TO NATION BUILDING</title>
      <para id="id1394612">MUSIC</para>
      <para id="id1395398">In this module we are going to sing and accompany South African songs in different languages from different cultures. These songs are all related to our theme: <emphasis effect="bold">nation building</emphasis>.</para>
