            <item>What is a rietkooi? Does it have anything to do with the Alibama as such? Motivate.</item>
            <item>Which other songs can be added to these?</item>
            <item>Do you agree with the expression “Ghoema is Woema”? Motivate.</item>
            <item>From what has the word “ghommaliedjie” been derived?</item>
            <item>Define the word “ghommaliedjie”.</item>
            <item>What is the most important musical element of ghoema moppie music?</item>
            <item>From what has the word “moppie” been derived?</item>
            <item>Give a definition of the word “moppie”.</item>
            <item>What is the difference between a moppie and a ghomma song?</item>
